title: Miles Davis - Get Up With It

---------------------------------------------------------------------------------
In my own opinion, i think this is one of the best album by Miles Davis. From 1969 to 1975 he developed his own unique style and is the best period of his music.A mixture of hard funk, psycadelic rock, avante-garde electronic jazz, that never been equaled. "Get It up With It", an album of such wilderness and lack of commercial forethoughts makes it rare and unique.
Download and enyoy this marvelous music and share it.
muzik62
